Acibadem Owner, Integrated Healthcare Plan Joint Venture

-- B y   A y d a n   E k s i n
-- 
2011-10-03T05:23:47Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/acibadem-owner-integrated-healthcare-plan-joint-venture.html
Integrated Healthare Holdings SDN BHD
and Acibadem Saglik Yatirimlari Holding AS, the owner of Turkish
hospital chain Acibadem Saglik Hizmetleri & Ticaret AS, signed a
non-binding agreement to set up a joint venture.  Intergrated Healtcare and Acibadem Holding plan health
investments in the Middle East, east  Europe  and Asia-Pacific,
Acibadem Saglik said in a statement to the  Istanbul Stock
Exchange  after the market closed on Sept. 30. The companies will
hold talks and carry out due diligence work before signing final
agreements, Acibadem said.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Aydan Eksin at 
 aeksin@bloomberg.net  